                "invention-title": [
                    "Iron ore powder fluidization hydrogen reduction ironmaking system based on solar energy",
                    "一种基于太阳能的铁矿粉流态化氢气还原炼铁系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of new energy utilization and metallurgy, and discloses an iron ore powder fluidization hydrogen reduction ironmaking system based on solar energy, which comprises a multi-stage fluidized bed reaction unit, a heat exchange system and a dust remover, each stage of fluidized bed reaction unit comprises a solar composite optical heating system and a fluidized bed reactor; the solar composite optical heating system gathers and reflects sunlight into the fluidized bed reactor to heat materials in the fluidized bed reactor; the gas outlet of the first-stage fluidized bed reactor is sequentially connected with the heat exchange system, the dust remover and the gas inlet of the Nth-stage fluidized bed reactor through pipelines; and the heat exchange system is respectively connected with a material inlet of the first-stage fluidized bed reactor and a gas inlet of the Nth-stage fluidized bed reactor through pipelines. According to the invention, the utilization rate of hydrogen is greatly improved by adopting the multi-stage series fluidized bed reactor and a gas recycling technology, the efficient utilization of hydrogen is realized, and a novel green low-carbon ironmaking method based on solar energy is provided."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于新能源利用和冶金技术领域，公开了一种基于太阳能的铁矿粉流态化氢气还原炼铁系统，包括多级流化床反应单元、换热系统、除尘器；每一级流化床反应单元包括太阳能复合光学加热系统、流化床反应器；太阳能复合光学加热系统将太阳光聚集反射进入流化床反应器加热其中的物料；第一级流化床反应器的气体出口与换热系统、除尘器、第N级流化床反应器的气体入口通过管道依次连接；换热系统与第一级流化床反应器的物料入口、第N级流化床反应器的气体入口分别通过管道连接。本发明采用多级串联流化床反应器和气体循环利用技术大大提高了提高氢气的利用率，实现氢气的高效利用，提供了一种新的基于太阳能的绿色低碳炼铁方法。"
                }
            ]
